+Build: npm run build succeeds.
+Manual smoke test — Standalone builder:
+Navigate to /story (direct URL load — confirms Router wiring) → Build tab shows 5-C form + live preview.
+Fill title + 5 fields; preview updates each keystroke; copy buttons show toast and write to clipboard.
+Save → toast confirms, form clears, switches to Vault; card appears with formatted date.
+Search filters by title/character/context.
+Edit pencil → loads card back into Build form; Save now updates instead of inserting.
